# SDDE-model

Shared Python package for the Julia-wrapped SDDE solar dynamo model.

## Install (editable)

```bash
pip install -e /Users/ulzg/SABC/SDDE-model
```

## Usage

```python
from sdde_model import sn, sn_batch, summary_statistics
```
